content: "Che cosa ordinerà al ristorante?" "Penso del sushi."
translations: eng:What will he order at the restaurant﹖ I think some sushi
eng:What will she order at the restaurant﹖ I think some sushi
eng:What will you order at the restaurant﹖ I think some sushi
